name: Btracking
description: Btracking is owned and operated by Herce
overview: Btracking is owned and operated by Herceg Network inc. Founded in 2009, we first launched our GPS mobile tracking solution to provide businesses with a better means of managing their mobile workforce through their smartphones. We’ve delivered solutions across the globe, always with the intention of bringing innovative solutions to client challenges. Our business focus, is primarily considered on ROI for each client. With each deployment, whether it is satellite tracking of containers, smartphone workforce management or vehicle gps tracking, we delivered optimal value-add benefits for multinationals, government agencies, military or small businesses. Today, we offer a full range of GPS solutions servicing companies of all sizes, across all industries. Contact us today to see how we can support your organization. For more information visit http://www.btracking.com
